snippet.title: Killzone 2 - Behind The Bullet Interactive Ad - PS3 Gameplay
snippet.description:
So a while ago I browsed my entire PS3 PSN library and found few really nice gems which I'd love to keep before they'll gone forever.
Here's one of them - Killzone 2 Behind The bullet Interactive real time Ad released for free to test by players.
Watch entire video - I also added full developer commentary on Killzone 2 tech behind its stunnig graphics.
Enjoy!
